column5: No, not the elbow to elbow river fishing kind. The kind where the fish give you a thorough beat down!!!! Just that casting would wear me out never mind the gargantuan GT's!!!! Grab a bowl of popcorn something to drink and enjoy!!  <iframe width="560" height="315" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/DFh0iaJ5nPw" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
Almost a good as Perchin L.Erie and a few Sheephead thrown in. Nother dream trip on the list. Just tired me out watchin.
That was awesome to watch! Thanks for posting
Gotta love saltwater fishing! There's one more experience for the bucket list.  Thanks for posting that Dave.
That's pretty intense fishing , thanks for posting
Part 2!!! A lot of good vids on their channel including giant blue fin tuna.  <iframe width="560" height="315" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/i6D-fiQdlA8" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
And I thought that catching 2-3 pound largies on a Pop-R was fun
Now that's my kind of workout!!
